XPath_Parser for PHP
====================
:Author:    Nicolas Thouvenin
:Homepage:  http://github.com/touv/xpath_parser
:Email:     nthouvenin@gmail.com
:Key words: php, xpath
:language:  php


Description 
-----------

It's a PHP Class that can transform a xpath string to a structured array.


License
-------

AIT is licensed under the LGPL version 2. For more information, see the attached COPYING file.


Downloading
------------

XPath_Parser is currently hosted at GitHub. It's source code can be found at
http://github.com/touv/xpath_parser. PEAR's package can be found at http://pear.pxxo.net/get/

You can also use the Pear's Installer :

......................................
$ pear channel-discover pear.pxxo.net
$ pear install pxxo/xpath_parser
......................................


